INSERT INTO AMP_orders
  (order_recv_f_name, order_recv_l_name, order_recv_address1, order_recv_city, order_recv_state, order_recv_zipcode, order_recv_phone, order_recv_email, order_priority, order_date, order_status)
VALUES
  (
    {{ order_recv_f_name.text }},
    {{ order_recv_l_name.text }},
    {{ order_recv_address1.text }},
		{{ order_recv_city.text }},
		{{ order_recv_state.text }},
		{{ order_recv_zip.text }},
		{{ order_recv_phone.text }},
		{{ order_recv_email.text }},
		{{ order_priority.text }},
		{{ order_date.text }},
		{{ order_status.text }}
  );
	SELECT LAST_INSERT_ID();
